}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== ===Specifications=== *Processor: [[Realtek]] RTL8380M Multi-Layer Managed Switch :Controller with Embedded MIPS 4KEc @500MHz *Co-processor: Nuvoton MO516LDN to manage PoE *Flash/RAM: 32MB (SPI NOR) Flash, 128MB RAM (DDR3L) *8x Gigabit PoE+ Ethernet ports, 2x Gigabit Ethernet ports *120W PoE budget with 54V/2.4A power adapter or :190W PoE budget with 54V/3.7A power adapter
